info.title: Schema of Azure Data Manager for Agriculture events published to Azure Event Grid
info.description: Describes the schema of the Azure Data Manager for Agriculture Configuration events published to Azure Event Grid. This corresponds to the Data property of an EventGridEvent.

DataManagerForAgriApplicationDataChanged.description: Schema of the Data property of an EventGridEvent for a Microsoft.AgFoodPlatform.ApplicationDataChanged.V2 event.

partyId.description: Id of the party it belongs to.

source.description: Source of the farm operation data.

modifiedDateTime.description: Date-time when resource was last modified, sample format: yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ.

properties.description:
A list of key value pairs that describe the resource.
Only string and numeral values are supported.

eTag.description: The ETag value to implement optimistic concurrency.

createdDateTime.description: Date-time when resource was created, sample format: yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ.
